Q1. Create new user and at the same time you have to add the user into group
We can do this by using the following command: 
useradd -G groupname username

Q2. How to unzip the bz2 file?
We can do this by using the following command: 
bzip2 -d filename.bz2  
-d = decompress

Q3. Create archive + compressed file with extension bz2 and in that include some file with data & folder
We can do this by using the following command: 
tar -cfvj archive.tar.bz2 data_file_1 dat_file_2

Q4. Add user and at the same time change the shell of the user to /bin/sh
We can do this by using the following command: 
useradd -s /bin/sh username


